{"tid":2230578,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"迫害宗教文件曝光 中共查洩密者","createTime":"2020-10-05T04:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T04:29:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0fccc87153b509968fcdc6f62e892c6b8106faf8","tid":2230578,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T04:27:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201005/PTG3JGCF4JCHXOFEQXMWDZTTHU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201005%2FPTG3JGCF4JCHXOFEQXMWDZTTHU%2F&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGAVsaiM9baN%2FEtUhsAXiQ7E%3D&h=430b424c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201005%2FPTG3JGCF4JCHXOFEQXMWDZTTHU%2F&h=9b815c43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201005/PTG3JGCF4JCHXOFEQXMWDZTTHU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n迫害宗教文件曝光 中共查洩密者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HJQ_BKaRrKv_hSPg1VdjPTOMqz0=/1051x591/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B2IYTR2IFJHTZHYMJHULRNUHME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHJQ_BKaRrKv_hSPg1VdjPTOMqz0%3D%2F1051x591%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FB2IYTR2IFJHTZHYMJHULRNUHME.jpg&h=f3a4e3fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《寒冬》常嚗光中共迫害宗教的文件。<br />\n<br />\n內地嚴查踢爆打壓宗教自由的洩密者。關注中國宗教自由問題的境外網站《寒冬》披露，各地都有宗教政策文件被海外媒體曝光，已驚動中央高層領導人，政府正「不惜一切代價」追查洩露文件的相關人員，一旦查明將予以重判，家人也會受牽連。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：暫延中梵協議 教廷：無外交目的  陳日君：扼殺教會如叛教<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嚴格審問教職人員<br />\n<br />\n多年來依賴報料人把情況曝光的《寒冬》指，由於中共愈發嚴格的監管措施，宗教人士揭露宗教被迫害事件正面臨越來越大的危險。華北某市當局近日傳喚當地百餘名基督教教職人員，就《寒冬》報道的政府宗教政策文件逐一審問。有知情人稱，雖然有關文件很普通，「在各教會都傳遍了，但政府很緊張。」<br />\n<br />\n一名被審訊的獲政府認可「三自」教堂同工說：「審訊非常嚴格，警察一遍又一遍問，問得很詳細，看這次回答的和上一次是否一致。」許多教堂負責人因懼怕政府追查，表示不敢再談論關於宗教迫害的事。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《寒冬》"},{"pid":"a73a8a7d012a4a863e6e1e5ea60686af5f17e3b4","tid":2230578,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"共產教宗：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/23CjPZa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F23CjPZa.png&h=6f87fb07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ffabb1f08663261676383f2d02b226e0a6d57b7","tid":2230578,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a73a8a7d012a4a863e6e1e5ea60686af5f17e3b4","tid":2230578,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"共產教宗：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/23CjPZa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F23CjPZa.png&h=6f87fb07&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T04:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XYr8Jjt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXYr8Jjt.jpg&h=fde4eae1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}